19#define RRTYPE_KX_ATTRIBUTES (0)

21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_in_kx(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_name_t name;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26
27 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
28 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
29
30 UNUSED(type);
31 UNUSED(rdclass);
32 UNUSED(callbacks);
33
34 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
35 false));
36 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
37 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
38 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
39
40 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
41 false));
42 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
43 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
44 if (origin == NULL)
45 origin = dns_rootname;
46 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
47 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
48}
49
50static inline isc_result_t
51totext_in_kx(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
52 isc_region_t region;
53 dns_name_t name;
54 dns_name_t prefix;
55 bool sub;
56 char buf[sizeof("64000")];
57 unsigned short num;
58
59 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
60 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
61 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
62
63 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
64 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
65
66 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
67 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
68 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
69 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
70 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
71
72 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
73
74 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
75 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
76 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
77}
78
79static inline isc_result_t
80fromwire_in_kx(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
81 dns_name_t name;
82 isc_region_t sregion;
83
84 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
85 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
86
87 UNUSED(type);
88 UNUSED(rdclass);
89
90 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
91
92 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
93
94 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
95 if (sregion.length < 2)
96 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
97 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sregion.base, 2));
98 isc_buffer_forward(source, 2);
99 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
100}
101
102static inline isc_result_t
103towire_in_kx(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
104 dns_name_t name;
105 dns_offsets_t offsets;
106 isc_region_t region;
107
108 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
109 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
110 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
111
112 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
113 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
114 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, 2));
115 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
116
117 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
118 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
119
120 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
121}
122
123static inline int
124compare_in_kx(ARGS_COMPARE) {
125 dns_name_t name1;
126 dns_name_t name2;
127 isc_region_t region1;
128 isc_region_t region2;
129 int order;
130
131 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
132 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
133 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
134 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
135 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
136 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
137
138 order = memcmp(rdata1->data, rdata2->data, 2);
139 if (order != 0)
140 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
141
142 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
143 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
144
145 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
146 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
147
148 isc_region_consume(&region1, 2);
149 isc_region_consume(&region2, 2);
150
151 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
152 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
153
154 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
155}
156
157static inline isc_result_t
158fromstruct_in_kx(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
159 dns_rdata_in_kx_t *kx = source;
160 isc_region_t region;
161
162 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
163 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
164 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
165 REQUIRE(kx->common.rdtype == type);
166 REQUIRE(kx->common.rdclass == rdclass);
167
168 UNUSED(type);
169 UNUSED(rdclass);
170
171 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(kx->preference, target));
172 dns_name_toregion(&kx->exchange, &region);
173 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
174}
175
176static inline isc_result_t
177tostruct_in_kx(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
178 isc_region_t region;
179 dns_rdata_in_kx_t *kx = target;
180 dns_name_t name;
181
182 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
183 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
184 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
185 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
186
187 kx->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
188 kx->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
189 ISC_LINK_INIT(&kx->common, link);
190
191 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
192 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
193
194 kx->preference = uint16_fromregion(&region);
195 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
196
197 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
198 dns_name_init(&kx->exchange, NULL);
199 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &kx->exchange));
200 kx->mctx = mctx;
201 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
202}
203
204static inline void
205freestruct_in_kx(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
206 dns_rdata_in_kx_t *kx = source;
207
208 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
209 REQUIRE(kx->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
210 REQUIRE(kx->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_kx);
211
212 if (kx->mctx == NULL)
213 return;
214
215 dns_name_free(&kx->exchange, kx->mctx);
216 kx->mctx = NULL;
217}
218
219static inline isc_result_t
220additionaldata_in_kx(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
221 dns_name_t name;
222 dns_offsets_t offsets;
223 isc_region_t region;
224
225 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
226 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
227
228 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
229 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
230 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
231 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
232
233 return ((add)(arg, &name, dns_rdatatype_a));
234}
235
236static inline isc_result_t
237digest_in_kx(ARGS_DIGEST) {
238 isc_region_t r1, r2;
239 dns_name_t name;
240
241 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
242 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
243
244 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r1);
245 r2 = r1;
246 isc_region_consume(&r2, 2);
247 r1.length = 2;
248 RETERR((digest)(arg, &r1));
249 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
250 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r2);
251 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
252}

254static inline bool
255checkowner_in_kx(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
256
257 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
258 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
259
260 UNUSED(name);
261 UNUSED(type);
262 UNUSED(rdclass);
263 UNUSED(wildcard);
264
265 return (true);
266}
267
268static inline bool
269checknames_in_kx(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
270
271 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_kx);
272 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
273
274 UNUSED(rdata);
275 UNUSED(owner);
276 UNUSED(bad);
277
278 return (true);
279}

281static inline int
282casecompare_in_kx(ARGS_COMPARE) {
283 return (compare_in_kx(rdata1, rdata2));
284}
